			<p><b>USS Massachusetts Operational Timeline</b></p><table border='0' cellspacing='0'><tr bgcolor='eeeeee'><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/07/20/1939' alt='See all events on 20 Jul 1939' title='See all events on 20 Jul 1939' class='noStyle'>20 Jul 1939</a>&nbsp;</td><td>The keel of battleship Massachusetts was laid down by the Bethlehem Steel Company in Quincy, Massachusetts, United States.</td></tr><tr bgcolor=''><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/05/12/1942' alt='See all events on 12 May 1942' title='See all events on 12 May 1942' class='noStyle'>12 May 1942</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Massachusetts was commissioned into service.</td></tr><tr bgcolor='eeeeee'><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/03/27/1947' alt='See all events on 27 Mar 1947' title='See all events on 27 Mar 1947' class='noStyle'>27 Mar 1947</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Massachusetts was decommissioned from service.</td></tr></table><br /><p><b>Photographs</b></p><table cellpadding='2' cellspacing='0' border='0'><tr><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=200'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_massachusetts5.jpg" border='0' alt='Battleship Massachusetts entering Boston Harbor, Massachusetts, United States, 12 May 1942'></a></td><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=200'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_massachusetts12.jpg" border='0' alt='Anti-aircraft gunfire seen above American ships against French fighters, off Casablanca, Morocco, early morning of 8 Nov 1942; seen from the after deck of battleship Massachusetts'></a></td><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=200'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_massachusetts11.jpg" border='0' alt='Battleship Massachusetts maneuvering off Casablanca, Morocco, 8 Nov 1942, as seen from destroyer Mayrant'></a></td><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&co